Titolo: Half-Life: Echoes

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: Half-Life: Echoes is a game modification of Half-Life created by British developer James "MrGnang" Coburn, released on August 10, 2018. The mod was under development for four years and uses the GoldSrc engine.Echoes is from the perspective of an unnamed scientist from the Black Mesa Research Facility as the resonance cascade happens and has the player fight unused monsters and the HECU with the G-Man and "Kingpin" observing the player.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
